title.narrative: Planning and programme strengthening in/on Fragile and Conflict Affected States.

description.narrative: This activity (Planning and programme strengthening in/on Fragile and Conflict Affected States.) is a component of Establishing a centre of excellence for Conflict and Stabilisation activity related to fragile and conflict affected states. reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £325,922. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Research/scientific institutions. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited, International Alert. The start date is 01-04-2013 and the end date is 31-03-2015.
